Currently supported and tested for the following plaforms and compilers:
Linux with:
         pgi/6.0-4
         pgi64/6.0-4  
         nag/5.0-361
         nag64/5.0-363        
         ifort/9.0.032
         ifort_em64t/9.0.032
Solaris with:
         Sun Studio 11 f90

To build GMIN:

1. Descend into src directory 

2. Modify Makefile COMPILERS AND COMPILER FLAGS section to choose the required values and type make.

4. Executable GMIN.2.2 will be generated.
